    "title": "Career Opportunity Software Engineer at Hexaware Technologies Global Group",
    "description": "Hexaware Technologies Global Group has an exciting opening for a Software Engineer at our Amritsar office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Hexaware Technologies Global Group:\nHexaware Technologies Global Group is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in React\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Amritsar, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Hexaware Technologies Global Group!",
